"System(BCM5351)V1.2_2009-05-13" is silkscreened on the module. This would seem to imply the device is BCM5351 based.
There is a MAC label on the SoC board with a 00:08:9F OUI ('''EFM Networks'''). '''EFM Networks''''s brand is '''ipTIME''', which seems to mostly sell '''Zioncom''' equipment.
